Lumber production, imports, exports, and consumption, by softwoods and hardwoods, 1965-1999.

Dataset containing statistics for lumber products. All units are in Billion Board ft. unless otherwise specified. All vectors are numeric.

pietc_l2

Format

A data frame with 56 observations of 15 variables:

Years
Years
Prod.Tot
Total Lumber Production
Prod.SW
Softwood Lumber Production
Prod.HW
Hardwood Lumber Production
Imports.Tot
Total Lumber Imports
Imports.SW
Softwood Lumber Imports
Imports.HW
Hardwood Lumber Imports
Exports.Tot
Total Lumber Exports
Exports.SW
Softwood Lumber Exports
Exports.HW
Hardwood Lumber Exports
Consump.Tot
Total Lumber Consumption
Consump.SW
Softwood Lumber Consumption
Consump.HW
Hardwood Lumber Consumption
PerCapConsump.Tot
Total Per Capita Consumption, in Board ft.
PerCapConsump.SW
Softwood Per Capita Consumption, in Board ft.
PerCapConsump.HW
Hardwood Per Capita Consumption, in Board ft.
